| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2024-3159 — Recovery Inhibition (embargo)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 6f82c20c-3e3c-50da-b2bf-1dc9efa36870"
